<emphasis box="[758,840,296,319]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="95">pinguis</emphasis>
and 
<emphasis box="[902,1017,296,320]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="95">foliaceous</emphasis>
, reference to the aedeagus medially expanded in lateral view.
</paragraph>
